    <item>
      <title>Version 1.2.0</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <ul>
          <li>Adds support for the new <strong>Grid</strong> controls, including app-aware Grid switching from the iPhone and iPad app.</li>
          <li>Fixes the menu-bar <strong>Open Accessibility</strong> action so permission recovery opens macOS System Settings directly.</li>
          <li>Prevents duplicate companion copies from lingering after reinstalling or launching a test build.</li>
          <li>Improves setup and settings button labels for assistive technologies.</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
