    <item>
      <title>Version 1.0.3</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <ul>
          <li>First-run setup now asks for the <strong>Keyboard Shortcuts (Automation)</strong> permission up front, so gestures like the three-finger swipe work right away — no surprise prompt mid-gesture.</li>
          <li>A simpler, clearer first-run permission screen.</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
