    <item>
      <title>Version 1.0.2</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <ul>
          <li>New: an in-app <strong>Update Available</strong> button, so updating is one click right from the menu-bar window.</li>
          <li>Much lighter on battery — the app fully idles (zero CPU wakeups) when no iPhone is connected, and runs at full speed the moment one is.</li>
          <li>Now available in 12 languages, with clearer system permission prompts.</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
